Cost Explorer and Cost allocation tags
======================================

- View and analyze your costs and usage.
- Cost allocation tags
- After you or aws applies tags to AWS Resources and you activate those tags in the Billing and Cost Management, AWS generates a cost allocation report as a Comma Separated Value (CSV)


Exam Tips:
==========

    - Use tag to tag your Resources
    - configure tags for cost centers
    - Activate cost allocation tags to track your costs by tags
    - Comes up frequents in sysops exam